==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: bù rù hǔxuè, yān dé hǔ zǐ

===Etymology===
Literally: If you don't enter the tiger's den, how will you get the tiger's cub?

===Proverb===
'''[[不]][[入]][[虎穴]]，[[焉]][[得]][[虎]][[子]]'''

# [[no risk, no reward]]; [[Nothing ventured, nothing gained]]

